div.div:
Adds a simple click handler to a button. Event objects are ignored.

$('#myButton').on('click', function() {
   window.alert('Button clicked!');
});

Adds a handler to all divs that paints their background color to red when clicked.

$('div').on('click', function() {
   this.style.backgroundColor = 'red';    // 'this' contains the element that caused the event
});
